{"_id":"nhsdeathguard001","name":"Spirit Shroud (Concealed in Horde)","type":"effect","img":"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-power.webp","system":{"slug":"spirit-shroud-concealed","description":{"value":"<p>You are sharing a space with a Deathguard necrologist's horde. The press of twisted limbs and swirling ectoplasm hides you from view, making you @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W]{Concealed} to all creatures.</p><p><em>Applied automatically by the Necrologist Horde Sync module when an ally shares the horde's space. Removed automatically when the ally leaves.</em></p>"},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"level":{"value":1},"duration":{"value":-1,"unit":"unlimited","sustained":false,"expiry":null},"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"badge":null,"context":null,"start":{"value":0,"initiative":null},"unidentified":false,"rules":[{"key":"GrantItem","uuid":"Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.DmAIPqOBomZ7H95W","onDeleteActions":{"granter":"restrict"}}]},"flags":{"necrologist-horde-sync":{"bundled":true}}}
